query: SELECT u.id as userId, u.email, u.openId, r.id as routeId, r.name as routeName, r.userId as routeOwnerId FROM users u LEFT JOIN routes r ON r.userId = u.id WHERE u.email = 'scheduling@prairiept.com' ORDER BY r.id DESC LIMIT 10
